The Local Legend Foundation is official.

The Foundation is a nonprofit organization dedicated to being a bridge between athletes, public figures and entrepreneurs or “Local Legends” to the community to make an impact. We hope that all of you will join us in our mission to give back directly to those facing mental, physical, or emotional adversity. Anyone who donates $35.00 by Nov 28th will receive an Official Local Legend SnapBack. Head over to the Foundation page for more information, link in bio!

Really blessed to announce The Local Legend Foundation (@locallegendfoundation).
Having the platform and opportunity to give back to the community is something that I am grateful for. The adversity I faced along my journey has inspired me to take action by being a mentor to our youth and young adults! 

The Foundation is a nonprofit organization dedicated to being a bridge between athletes, public figures and entrepreneurs or “Local Legends” to the community to make an impact. Happy Holidays!
